dc_description_s: These sets of data include the drinking water supply management area boundaries and the vulnerability levels within each management area in Minnesota. More information can be found at: http://www.health.state.mn.us/divs/eh/water/swp/maps/index.htm Follow the links below to the access the individual metadata pages for each layer: Drinking Water Supply Management Areas: drinking_water_supply_management_areas.html Drinking Water Supply Management Areas Vulnerability: drinking_water_supply_management_area_vulnerability.html
dc_title_s: Drinking Water Supply Management Areas: Minnesota, 2014
